{"tid":2489055,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大亞灣核電廠每年向香港排放的核廢水  放射性含量是福島核廢水的十倍","createTime":"2021-04-14T16:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T19:37:56.000Z","uid":391580,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cda295294376da5208680711eb85ea81009093b8","tid":2489055,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"日本政府決定兩年後，將福島第一核電廠的核廢水排入大海，連日來引起中韓反對。中國官方連番炮轟，外交部發言人趙立堅稱，海洋不是日本的垃圾桶：「個別官員稱『這些水喝了也沒事』，請他喝了再說。」<br />\n<br />\n《眾新聞》翻查資料，發現中國現存的49座核電機組，同樣有將核廢水倒落大海。其中最接近香港的大亞灣核電站，放射性物質「氚」的排放上限，甚至比日本福島的排放標準高出十倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU1MgHgz5gvHcVzEuMqJD9WMpmVGdvcY8M1uM9rmvMc6C?filename=ZVuax07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVuax07.jpg&h=60f9adb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbexiR9EXhsWcPD7TcvFDTtuE8xbqjNjxDUvr2Nrf6Ee?filename=YEKqmUH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEKqmUH.jpg&h=e4b86ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb3nMRedbHVCy8BDPXdxero3jS4se39aoLDfQ9WbxaeA9?filename=n2D6QN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2D6QN3.jpg&h=cda35ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據內地生態環境部在2017年的一份批文，大亞灣核電基地共六台機組，每年的液態氚排放上限達到225兆貝克，是福島未來每年排放量的十倍。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港核電投資公司（HKNIC）數據顯示，過去十年，大亞灣核電站的液態氚排放量平均為上限的20%，即是約49.5兆貝克。若與日本政府訂出的標準比較，是超出一倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n內地其他核電廠又如何？以秦山核電廠為例，廠方在2008年曾經向生態環境部請示每年排放核廢水的標準，光是第一二期和擴建的機組，液態氚的排放量上限就達到125兆，是現在福島訂出的排放量5倍多。根據公開文件，國家核安全局回覆指，這個數量可以接受，所以予以批准。福建福清核電廠的排放上限，同樣超出福島標準。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年底，內地已經有16間核電廠，一共49座核電機組正在運作中。光是香港的方圓200公里內已有4座核電廠，包括大亞灣、嶺澳、台山和陽江。究竟他們每年排放多少核廢水？當局沒有公開整體數字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40276/%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%9E%E7%81%A3%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%99-%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%99%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%85-40276/%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F40276%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%259E%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B6%2599%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%2585-40276%2F%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=25f25164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40276/%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%9E%E7%81%A3%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%99-%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E8%B6%99%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%85-40276/%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a>"},{"pid":"a56ed6bd9f51e7f1c27cdc0fc68c0156d9bcd3f1","tid":2489055,"uid":123738,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"講元素邊有人贏到支那呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗隻隻都食元素大"},{"pid":"586d6f2fbcf0043307764f51a369362f7667a3bc","tid":2489055,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e86dd44b46113e5e2947e14b4b4f258eb25d1f","tid":2489055,"uid":259901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"大亞灣核電廠排放數據係歷史文件，中方已經完成